	'Configure the behavior of Drop Targets.
Const DTDropSpeed = 110 'in milliseconds
Const DTDropUpSpeed = 40 'in milliseconds
Const DTDropUnits = 80 'VP units primitive drops so top of at or below the playfield
Const DTDropUpUnits = 20 'VP units primitive raises above the up position on drops up
Const DTMaxBend = 8 'max degrees primitive rotates when hit
Const DTDropDelay = 20 'time in milliseconds before target drops (due to friction/impact of the ball)
Const DTRaiseDelay = 10 'time in milliseconds before target drops back to normal up position after the solenoid fires to raise the target
